Central European Media’s TV Nova Seeks License for New Channel

-- B y   L e n k a   P o n i k e l s k a
-- 
2011-08-17T15:15:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-17/central-european-media-s-tv-nova-seeks-license-for-new-channel.html
Central European Media Ltd.’s TV
Nova is seeking a license for a new channel from the Czech
Council for Radio and Television Broadcasting, Mediar.cz
reported, citing the head of the council Katerina Kalistova. The
new channel will be aimed at attracting a male audience, the web
site focused on media issues in the  Czech Republic  added.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lenka Ponikelska in Prague at 
 lponikelska1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  